title: Readout of the President’s Call with Abu Dhabi Crown Prince Sheikh Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
September 05, 2015

 



Readout of the President’s Call with Abu Dhabi Crown Prince Sheikh Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan





	President Obama spoke today by phone with the Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi, Sheikh Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, to offer deep condolences for the loss of 45 Emirati service members in Yemen on September 4, 2015. The thoughts and prayers of the American people are with the people of the UAE and with the families of the fallen.
